name: Op in
tagline: A place for Open Information sharing, focused on public liberty
body:
### Welcome to the Op In project github page.
This page is a template for the Op In project information.

### Participation
We would be very pleased to welcome any who are willing and able to help develop content with this content, to enable others to examine options for benefiting themselves and their communities.
